title: Large collection of quality Clipart.  All eps files
description:
This is a cleaned up version of 'clipart explosion' that I originally downloaded from here.  The original, when unzipped, expanded to gigabytes of excess copies.  This version will give you one copy.  

The list includes items from "A" to "I".  Advertising, Agriculture, Alphabets, Americana, Anatomy, Animals, Antique, Architecture, Arrows, Art, Backgrounds, Beauty, Borders, Brush Strokes, Business, Buttons, Calendar, Cartoons, Clothing, Computers, Construction, Crests, Education, Electrical, Electronics, Energy, Engineering, Entertainment, Fantasy, Fitness, Flags, Food, Furniture, Gardening, Government, Graphs, Hands, Health, Holidays, Household, Interior, International.

I don't know if there is more out there from this collection.  If there is please upload it and seed.

Check my other upload for the .eps thumbnail viewer so you can see the thumbnails in Windows.
